<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٤١ ... سُورَةُ فُصِّلَتْ ... آياتها ٥٤ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فُصِّلَتْ}</span> ... بُيِّنَتْ آيَاتُهُ، وَوُضِّحَتْ مَعَانِيهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَكِنَّةٍ}</span> ... أَغْطِيَةٍ مَانِعَةٍ مِنْ فَهْمِ مَا تَدْعُونَا إِلَيْهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَقْرٌ}</span> ... صَمَمٌ، وَثِقَلٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَاسْتَقِيمُوا إِلَيْهِ}</span> ... اسْلُكُوا الطَّرِيقَ المُوصِلَ إِلَيْهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَوَيْلٌ}</span> ... هَلَاكٌ، وَعَذَابٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَيْرُ مَمْنُونٍ}</span> ... غَيْرُ مَقْطُوعٍ، وَلَا مَمْنُوعٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَندَادًا}</span> ... شُرَكَاءَ، وَنُظَرَاءَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَوَاسِيَ}</span> ... جِبَالًا ثَوَابِتَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَقْوَاتَهَا}</span> ... أَرْزَاقَ أَهْلِهَا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِي أَرْبَعَةِ أَيَّامٍ}</span> ... يَوْمَانِ لِخَلْقِ الأَرْضِ، وَيَوَمْانِ لِخَلْقِ الرَّوَاسِي، وَتَقْدِيرِ الأَقْوَاتِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَوَاءً}</span> ... فِي تَمَامِ أَرْبَعَةِ أَيَّامٍ مُسْتَوِيَةٍ؛ بِلَا زِيَادة، وَلَا نُقْصَانٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اسْتَوَى}</span> ... قَصَدَ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَقَضَاهُنَّ}</span> ... فَخَلَقَهُنَّ، وَأَبْدَعَهُنَّ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِمَصَابِيحَ}</span> ... بِنُجُومٍ مُضِيئَةٍ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَحِفْظًا}</span> ... حَرَسًا مِنَ الشَّيَاطِينِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>